<div id="pf4460" class="pf w4f h2fe" data-page-no="4460"><div class="pc pc4460 w4f h2fe"><div class="t m165c xb7 h5 y2f11 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 7 August 12-18 </div><div class="t m9a4 x0 h13a y2b76 ff3 fs50 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The </div><div class="t mf3a x58 h2e1 y2b4f ff2 fs50 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Spirit </div><div class="t m2a0 x11 h5 y16f ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;I will pray the Father, and he shall </div><div class="t m2f1 x3 h5 ya9 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">give you another Comforter, that he </div><div class="t m7fb x3 h5 y146d ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">may abide with you for ever&quot; (John </div><div class="t m83b x3 h5 y3eb ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">14:16). </div><div class="t m828 x11 h35 ye05 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Holy Spirit plays such an </div><div class="t m433 xbd h35 y1cc ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">important role in the plan of salvation </div><div class="t m7cc x3 h35 y69f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and is so vitally related to our </div><div class="t m4da xbd h35 yd8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">preparation for the final crisis and the </div><div class="t m979 xbd h35 ydea ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">finishing of God&apos;s work in this earth </div><div class="t m12c xbd h35 y5eb ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that He merits a careful consideration </div><div class="t m900 xbd h35 y31a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">in this series of lessons. </div><div class="t m9f7 x11 h35 y6ed ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">On the other hand, the Spirit&apos;s real </div><div class="t m2c5 xbd h35 y19e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">nature and function have been </div><div class="t m17c xbd h35 y8e2 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">wrongly interpreted by many. It is of </div><div class="t m7a6 xbd h35 y155 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the utmost importance, therefore, to </div><div class="t me5f xbd h35 y102 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">clarify our concepts about Him, His </div><div class="t m594 xbd h35 y1f9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">essence, His power, His relationship </div><div class="t m148b xbd h35 y9ac ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to God, to Christ, and to the Word of </div><div class="t m241 xbd h35 y5d4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God—as well as His relationship to us </div><div class="t m6d5 xbd h35 y605 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and the tremendous task He will </div><div class="t m999 xbd h35 y11 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">perform in this last stage of human </div><div class="t m12f4 xbd h35 y1a4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">history. </div><div class="t m532 x17 h35 ybf ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The outstanding importance of the </div><div class="t m4a6 xbd h35 y658 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">work of the Holy Spirit is reflected in </div><div class="t maa xbd h35 y91d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">these words of the servant of the Lord: </div><div class="t mae1 x4 h35 y2a8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;This promised blessing [the </div><div class="t m825 x4 h35 yc56 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">reception of the Holy Spirit], claimed </div><div class="t m3dc x4 h35 y1b53 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">by faith, brings all other blessings in its </div><div class="t m110f x4 h35 y96f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">train.&quot;—Gospel </div><div class="t m2f0 xf h35 y237 ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Workers, </div><div class="t m1b5 x6a h3c y237 ff2 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">p. </div><div class="t m459 x77 h35 y237 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">285. It is </div><div class="t m2ae x4 h35 y162 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">like a great package of spiritual goods </div><div class="t m4ad x4 h35 y324 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that wraps up all the wonderful </div><div class="t m6ee x4 h35 y61a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">blessings of heaven. And the beautiful </div><div class="t m736 x4 h35 y505 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">thing about Him is that Christ has </div><div class="t m6fe x4 h35 y2d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">promised to send Him to guide us, to </div><div class="t m888 x4 h35 y7d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">strengthen us, to be present with us, </div><div class="t m55a x4 h35 ydee ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to transform us and make us victorious </div><div class="t m3e2 x4 h35 y15b8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">over sin, and to empower us for the </div><div class="t me61 x4 h35 y279 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">finishing of the gospel proclamation. </div><div class="t m3c8 x3e h35 y5e8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Nevertheless, unless we understand </div><div class="t mb7f x4 h35 y629 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">His nature and mission in our life and </div><div class="t me66 x4 h35 y40 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">in the church, and unless we prepare  </div><div class="t m9da x5a h35 y16f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">our hearts for His abiding presence, </div><div class="t m416 x5a h35 ya9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">we cannot receive the benefits that </div><div class="t m750 x5a h35 y1ef ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">come from His company and power. </div><div class="t m1452 x5a h35 y3eb ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Our life will lack the quality and the </div><div class="t mc8 x5a h35 y5e0 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">depth which the times in which we live </div><div class="t m724 x5a h35 y22a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">require of us. </div><div class="t m81f x7 h35 y14e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Naturally, our inquiry about the </div><div class="t ma7a x5a h35 y55a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Holy Spirit will not be a complete </div><div class="t m787 x5a h35 y1b7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">theological discussion of the matter, </div><div class="t m6ad xb0 h35 y212 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">but rather a personal and </div><div class="t m7dc x5a h35 y8c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">experimental knowledge of what God </div><div class="t m336 xb0 h35 y3f0 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">can and will do in our life through His </div><div class="t m659 x5a h35 y402 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">work. </div><div class="t mf5e x7 h35 y19d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In this lesson—the first of four </div><div class="t m13a xb0 h35 y8e3 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">consecutive ones devoted to this </div><div class="t m5a9 xb0 h35 y1d5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">supreme subject—we shall study the </div><div class="t m121 xb0 h35 y404 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Holy Spirit as the Third Person of the </div><div class="t m85 xb0 h35 y2bd ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Godhead. We shall demonstrate that </div><div class="t m6d2 xb0 h35 y1fa ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">He is a person, that He is the </div><div class="t m2e8 xb0 h35 y5ed ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">representative of God and of Christ. </div><div class="t m85d xb0 h35 y60 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Then we shall review His many </div><div class="t me12 xb0 h35 ya27 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">beneficial functions in our life. </div><div class="t m14a xb0 h5 y21a ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DAILY HIGHLIGHTS </div><div class="t m23f xb0 h5 y658 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m295 x4b h5 y658 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Godhead: A Perfect Unity </div><div class="t ma78 x4b h5 y58a ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Matt. 28:19; 2 Cor. 13:14) </div><div class="t m558 xb0 h5 ye8 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m457 x4b h5 ye8 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">A Person </div><div class="t mea5 x4b h5 y321 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Eph. 4:30) </div><div class="t mb7 xb0 h5 yba0 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m9a1 x4b h5 y617 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">A Representative </div><div class="t m77e x4b h5 y238 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(John 16:7) </div><div class="t m1ce x6e h5 y33f ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m418 x4b h5 ycf9 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Functions-1 </div><div class="t m77e x4b h5 y8f1 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(John 16:8) </div><div class="t m8a8 xb0 h5 y5f0 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t m39c x4b h5 y5f0 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Functions-2 </div><div class="t m9be xab h5 y773 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rom. 8:26, 27) </div><div class="t m2ef xb0 h5 y7b ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t m1d8 x4b h5 y7b ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Presence in the Life </div><div class="t m4ff x4b h5 y457 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(1 Cor. 3:16, 17) </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
